.SH NAME
hopsh @RELEASE@ \- send a command to a running Hop server.

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hopsh
[ options ]
[ \fIinput\fR ]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
\fBHopsh\fR is a tool that let users spawn \fBhop\fR from a command
line interface.
.SH OPTIONS

.TP 10
options
Many options are available. Type `hopsh -help' to print them.

The complete \fBHopsh\fR documentation is available as a Web application. 
To access this documentation, starts the server and browse the url 

   http://localhost:8080/hop/doc

.SH "SEE ALSO"
hop(1), hopreplay(1)

